text: Asghar Ali Khan is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament for Gaibandha-2. ==Career== Khan retired as a Major from Bangladesh Army. He was elected to parliament from Gaibandha-2 as a candidate in 1988. He contested the 1996 election from Gaibandha-3 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Bangladesh Army officers Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
